premise_source_doc_sentence: NASA 's newest spacecraft , the Orion Multi-Purpose Crew Vehicle  (  MPCV  )  , will be the first American spacecraft since Project Apollo to use an escape system in the event of a launch abort , something its predecessor , the Space Shuttle , had for only its first four orbital test flights in 1981-1982 .
